Fourth Department,

September, 1956 *

(September 19, 1956) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Louis Battice, Appellant, against Robert Murphy, as Warden, Respondent.

Not published with other decisions of September 19, 1956, ante, p. 827. - [Rep.

Motion to appeal on handwritten papers denied on the ground that habeas corpus is not the proper remedy.
